public interface IApplicantService
Defines the operations related to managing applicant data in the BTOMS

  • Method Details

    • createApplicant

      Applicant createApplicant(String nric, String name, int age, String maritalStatus, String password)
      Creates a new applicant and adds them to the system.
      Parameters:
      nric - The NRIC of the applicant.
      name - The name of the applicant.
      age - The age of the applicant.
      maritalStatus - The marital status of the applicant (e.g., "single", "married").
      password - The password for the applicant's account.
      Returns:
      The newly created Applicant object.

    • getApplicant

      Applicant getApplicant(String nric)
      Retrieves an applicant from the system by their NRIC.
      Parameters:
      nric - The NRIC of the applicant to retrieve.
      Returns:
      The Applicant object associated with the given NRIC, or null if no such applicant exists.

    • getAllApplicants

      Map<String,Applicant> getAllApplicants()
      Retrieves all applicants in the system.
      Returns:
      A map of all applicants, keyed by their NRIC.
